# Parts List — Stage 1 (VALK)


## Essential
- Pixhawk 2.4.8 flight controller
- Standard Pixhawk 2.4.8 Power Module (e.g., PM02 or equivalent) power module
- u-blox NEO-8 GPS module
- Telemetry radio (915 MHz or 433 MHz recommended for India)
- 4 × brushless motors (S500-class, e.g., 2212/920KV or similar)
- 4 × 30A ESCs (BLHeli)
- S500 (Holybro S500 V2) frame kit (frame, arms, PDB, props)
- 2 × LiPo batteries (4S, 5000–5200 mAh, ≥30C)
- LiPo balance charger (supports 4S, 5A recommended)
- XT60 connectors, wiring harness, heatshrink


## Recommended
- Spare arms, spare propellers
- Vibration-damping mount for Pixhawk
- Buzzer & safety switch
- Multimeter, zip ties, threadlocker


## Optional
- Landing gear extensions, camera mount, 5V 5A BEC (for Pi)
